arStrings.szText: You set a finger on this, and I’ll add it to my collection.
Frustrated, struggling to open a chest while another bandit watches over their shoulder.
Yeah, well, I called finder’s hand on it. The goods are mine.
Frustrated, struggling to open a chest while another bandit watches over their shoulder.
Don't tell me to hurry. Damn thing is rusted shut!
